Package Source

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CellInterface
    Interface for the cells of the goose game.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Board
    Board is the class that represents a Board.
    Cell
    Cell is the class that represents a Cell.
    Game
    Game is the class that represents the Goose Game itself A Game is characterized by the following informations : A board, which represents the the Goose Game's board An amount of players for the current Game.
    GooseCell
    GooseCell is the class that represents a Goose Cell.
    Player
    Player is the class that represents a Goose Game player.
    TeleportCell
    A Teleport Cell send the Player to a specific Cell.
    TrapCell
    A TrapCell keeps the player until the next event.
    WaitCell
    A WaitCell keeps the player for a number of turns.
